OL,3,CSocial media as dangerous for young
OL,4,Cpeople as smoking, top doctors warn
OL,6,FSocial media is the new smoking, top
OL,7,Fdoctors have warned, as pressure grows
OL,8,Fon the government to introduce a ban
OL,9,Ffor under-16s.
OL,11,FThe government's Growing Up In The
OL,12,FOnline World consultation, which
OL,13,Ffloated measures such as an Australia-
OL,14,Fstyle social media ban for under-16s,
OL,15,Fapp curfews and limits on addictive
OL,16,Ffeatures, closes at the end of
OL,17,FTuesday, with bereaved families set to
OL,18,Fmeet with the prime minister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
