OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779891067
OL,3,CSocial media as dangerous for young
OL,4,Cpeople as smoking, top doctors warn
OL,6,FA report by the Academy of Medical
OL,7,FRoyal Colleges, submitted to the
OL,8,Fpublic consultation, said social media
OL,9,Fand smartphone use "ranks alongside
OL,10,Fsmoking and wearing seatbelts in cars
OL,11,Fas a unifying force for the medical
OL,12,Fprofession".
OL,14,FDoctors are seeing a "wave of
OL,15,Fradicalised children" from exposure to
OL,16,F"hateful, addictive and grossly
OL,17,Fdistressing content", the report said.
OL,26,@qD@TOUtD@KO]vD@VOUwD@UO]xD@AOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
