CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779891067
OL,3,CSocial media as dangerous for young
OL,4,Cpeople as smoking, top doctors warn
OL,6,FOf the 454 doctors surveyed, half said
OL,7,Fthey treated at least one child a week
OL,8,Fwhose mental distress or physical
OL,9,Finjury was linked to online content.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FThe report included harrowing stories
OL,17,Fof deaths and injuries from
OL,18,F"replicating acts of extreme
OL,19,Fpornography" and interests in violence
OL,20,For radicalisation.
OL,26,@zD@AOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
