OL,3,CSocial media as dangerous for young
OL,4,Cpeople as smoking, top doctors warn
OL,6,FTechnology Secretary Liz Kendall said
OL,7,Flast month that proposals to restrict
OL,8,Fsocial media for under-16s would be
OL,9,Fput forward by the summer, with plans
OL,10,Fto legislate by the end of the year.
OL,12,FMinisters announced in April that they
OL,13,Fwould introduce "age or functionality
OL,14,Frestrictions" on social media for
OL,15,Funder-16s regardless of the
OL,16,Fconsultation outcome.
OL,26,@uD@QOUvD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779891067
OL,3,CSocial media as dangerous for young
OL,4,Cpeople as smoking, top doctors warn
OL,6,FPeers have voted multiple times to
OL,7,Fpress the Commons into accepting a
OL,8,Fsocial media ban, ending their stand-
OL,9,Foff with MPs only after ministers
OL,10,Fagreed to restrictions.
OL,12,FTory former education minister and
OL,13,Facademy chain founder, Lord Nash,
OL,14,Furged the government to "get on with
OL,15,Fit".
OL,17,F"The Government gave a commitment to
OL,18,FParliament that they would introduce
OL,19,Fsome form of age or functionality
OL,20,Frestriction on social media for
OL,21,Fchildren under 16," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779891067
OL,3,CSocial media as dangerous for young
OL,4,Cpeople as smoking, top doctors warn
OL,6,F"We now expect them to deliver on that
OL,7,Fcommitment fully and in the shortest
OL,8,Fpossible timeframe."
OL,10,FFamilies who have lost relatives to
OL,11,Fharm linked to online platforms are
OL,12,Fset to meet Sir Keir Starmer on
OL,13,FTuesday and urge him to honour the
OL,14,Fgovernment's promise.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
