FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779891067
OL,3,CSocial media as dangerous for young
OL,4,Cpeople as smoking, top doctors warn
OL,6,FEllen Roome, who believes her son
OL,7,FJools Sweeney died aged 14 while
OL,8,Fattempting an online challenge, said:
OL,9,F"I, and other families who have lost
OL,10,Fchildren to social media, will tell
OL,11,Fthe Prime Minister directly: Social
OL,12,Fmedia is a product, and like any other
OL,13,Ffaulty product causing the deaths of
OL,14,Fchildren, it should be restricted
OL,15,Funtil the companies responsible have
OL,16,Ffixed it and proven it is safe.
OL,18,F"We cannot go on with further
OL,19,Fspeculation ` we need clarity."
OL,26,@qD@AOUzD@AOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779891067
OL,3,CSocial media as dangerous for young
OL,4,Cpeople as smoking, top doctors warn
OL,6,FBut another coalition of children's
OL,7,Forganisations warned that focusing
OL,8,Fsolely on age limits risked failing to
OL,9,Faddress the structural drivers of
OL,10,Fonline harms.
OL,12,FThe Children's Coalition for Online
OL,13,FSafety, led by 5Rights Foundation and
OL,14,Fincluding groups such as the NSPCC and
OL,15,FGirlguiding, demanded a broader
OL,16,Foverhaul of technology companies'
OL,17,Fbusiness models and product design
OL,18,Fchoices that keep young users hooked.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779891067
OL,3,CSocial media as dangerous for young
OL,4,Cpeople as smoking, top doctors warn
OL,6,FIn a joint statement, 25 organisations
OL,7,Fcalled for a ban on targeted
OL,8,Fadvertising and manipulative design
OL,9,Ffeatures; a ban on personalised
OL,10,Fservices for under-13s and default
OL,11,Fsafety protections for under-16s with
OL,12,Fpenalties for firms that fall short;
OL,13,Fstronger regulation of AI systems,
OL,14,Fincluding child-focused risk
OL,15,Fassessments; and the creation of an
OL,16,Findependent online safety commissioner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779891067
OL,3,CSocial media as dangerous for young
OL,4,Cpeople as smoking, top doctors warn
OL,6,FLeanda Barrington-Leach, executive
OL,7,Fdirector at 5Rights Foundation, said:
OL,8,F"We will not fix this by tinkering
OL,9,Faround the edges ` by tweaking
OL,10,Ffeatures or relying on age limits
OL,11,Falone.
OL,13,F"The issue is not a single product or
OL,14,Fsetting; it is built into the system
OL,15,Fitself, into business models and
OL,16,Fdesign choices that prioritise
OL,17,Fengagement, data extraction and profit
OL,18,Fover children's wellbeing.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779891067
OL,3,CSocial media as dangerous for young
OL,4,Cpeople as smoking, top doctors warn
OL,6,F"If a product were unsafe for children
OL,7,Foffline, it would not be allowed onto
OL,8,Fthe market. We must insist on this
OL,9,Fsame logic online.
OL,11,F"The onus must be on these businesses
OL,12,Fto demonstrate that their services are
OL,13,Fsafe for children and not on parents
OL,14,For children to navigate or manage that
OL,15,Frisk themselves."
OL,17,FThe NSPCC charity said tech companies
OL,18,Fprioritising profit over keeping
OL,19,Fchildren safe "cannot be allowed to
OL,20,Fcontinue".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@QO]{D@OOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779891067
OL,3,CSocial media as dangerous for young
OL,4,Cpeople as smoking, top doctors warn
OL,6,FA Government spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Everyone ` especially children and
OL,8,Fyoung people ` should be able to have
OL,9,Fa positive, safe experience online.
OL,11,F"That's why we are consulting on a
OL,12,Fwide range of measures, from
OL,13,Frestricting social media access to
OL,14,Fpotential app curfews, to ensure we
OL,15,Fget the balance right and protect
OL,16,Fyoung people from harm.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779891067
OL,3,CSocial media as dangerous for young
OL,4,Cpeople as smoking, top doctors warn
OL,6,F"We are still seeking views from
OL,7,Fparents, young people and experts
OL,8,Fbefore taking our next steps. More
OL,9,Fthan 70,000 people have already
OL,10,Fengaged, and there is still time for
OL,11,Fothers to share their views before the
OL,12,Fconsultation closes at midnight.
OL,14,F"We are also taking wider action to
OL,15,Ftackle online harm. Through the Online
OL,16,FSafety Act, platforms have to give
OL,17,Fusers more control over the content
OL,18,Fthey see and stronger protections from
OL,19,Fharmful material."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU{D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
